name: Janice Griffith
description:
Janice Griffith

She left us too soon...indeed she's left the industry and is now living out her life as one of the most beautiful goddesses to grace our eyes.

I ran 6,000 steps and have settled on the 3400-step version.

Built on top of v1.5; as usual she looks best on all of the nicer Models available here.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!
